{"tid":1949912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[醫療爆煲]確診酒吧員工24小時仍未送院 單位一劏五 另有四家庭居住","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T04:12:12.000Z","uid":73883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c71ce7c34e854349dc02f95ba5a944813e02b1","tid":1949912,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"本港今日（29日）新增59宗新型冠狀病毒確診，累計個案達641宗；醫管局承認有部分人確診後，等逾一日仍未能送院。油尖旺區議員李國權向本報表示，接獲一名21歲男患者（個案567）求助，他於尖沙嘴一間酒吧工作，昨晚（28日）獲通知確診，但衛生署至今晚8時仍未安排他送院。本報正向醫管局查詢。<br />\n<br />\n李國權表示，病人與母親同住深水埗基隆街101號一個劏房，單位一劏五，另有4個家庭，病人希望能盡早入院，亦擔心母親會受感染，冀能盡快將母親送走。他說，劏房內其他家庭得悉後很擔憂，不斷清潔消毒單位，只敢留在家中。他亦關注劏房住戶感染風險，促請當局盡快安排患者送院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200329/s00001/1585484925000/21%e6%ad%b2%e5%8a%8f%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6%e6%98%a8%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba%e4%bb%8a%e6%99%9a%e4%bb%8d%e6%9c%aa%e9%80%81%e9%99%a2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200329%2Fs00001%2F1585484925000%2F21%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%258a%258f%25e6%2588%25bf%25e6%2588%25b6%25e6%2598%25a8%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%2599%259a%25e4%25bb%258d%25e6%259c%25aa%25e9%2580%2581%25e9%2599%25a2&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqwx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=a76dd6e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200329%2Fs00001%2F1585484925000%2F21%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%258a%258f%25e6%2588%25bf%25e6%2588%25b6%25e6%2598%25a8%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e4%25bb%258a%25e6%2599%259a%25e4%25bb%258d%25e6%259c%25aa%25e9%2580%2581%25e9%2599%25a2&h=fcee8b1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200329/s00001/1585484925000/21%e6%ad%b2%e5%8a%8f%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6%e6%98%a8%e7%a2%ba%e8%a8%ba%e4%bb%8a%e6%99%9a%e4%bb%8d%e6%9c%aa%e9%80%81%e9%99%a2</a>"},{"pid":"49dbb17765cf81282e3d40033b594edfc6059d75","tid":